#: templates/contact.html:18
msgid "e-tacは、多種多様な受託業務を通じて製造現場の運営ノウハウの蓄積を行ってまいりました。"
msgstr ""
"Through a wide range of contract services, e-tac has accumulated operational"
" expertise in manufacturing environments."

#: templates/contact.html:19
msgid "「業種」「業態」「企業」各々、取り組んでいる業務や方向性が異なるように、問題点も異なります。"
msgstr ""
"Just as the specific tasks and strategic directions vary across different "
"“Industries,” “Business models,” and “Companies,” so do the challenges they "
"face."

#: templates/contact.html:20
msgid "e-tacは、現場理解を最優先に考えております。課題や問題点、目指す方向を理解させていただいた上で、貴社に最適なご提案をいたします。"
msgstr ""
"At e-tac, we prioritize understanding your specific situation. After gaining"
" a clear understanding of your challenges, issues, and goals, we will "
"provide you with the solution that best suits your company."

#: templates/contact.html:21
msgid "e-tacは、焦ることなく着実に取り組みます。"
msgstr "e-tac takes a steady, methodical approach without rushing."

#: templates/contact.html:22
msgid "e-tacとの出会いが企業成長の道しるべになることを約束いたします。"
msgstr ""
"We promise that your partner ship with e-tac will serve as a guide post for "
"your company’s growth."

