#: templates/privacy.html:19
msgid "個人情報の取扱いについて"
msgstr "Regarding the handling of Personal Information"

#: templates/privacy.html:23
msgid "当社は、お問い合わせ・採用募集等に際してご提供いただく個人情報について、以下の通り適切に取り扱います"
msgstr ""
"We will handle the personal information you provide to us in connection with"
" inquiries, job applications, and other matters appropriately, as outlined "
"below"

#: templates/privacy.html:29
msgid "取得する個人情報"
msgstr "Personal Information Collected"

#: templates/privacy.html:31
msgid "当社は、氏名、会社名、連絡先、メールアドレス、住所、その他お問い合わせに含まれる情報を取得する場合があります。"
msgstr ""
"We may collect information such as your name, company name, contact "
"information, email address, mailing address, and other details included in "
"your inquiry."

#: templates/privacy.html:37
msgid "利用目的"
msgstr "Purpose of Use"

#: templates/privacy.html:40
msgid "取得した個人情報は、以下の目的のために利用いたします。"
msgstr ""
"We will use the personal information we collect for the following purposes."

#: templates/privacy.html:44
msgid "お問い合わせへの回答"
msgstr "Response to your Inquiry"

#: templates/privacy.html:48
msgid "ご依頼・ご相談への対応"
msgstr "Handling Requests and Inquiries"

#: templates/privacy.html:52
msgid "採用選考および関連する連絡"
msgstr "Recruitment Process and Related Communications"

#: templates/privacy.html:56
msgid "サービス改善・品質向上"
msgstr "Service Improvement and Quality Enhancement"

#: templates/privacy.html:60
msgid "当社サービス・関連情報のご案内"
msgstr "Information About Our Services and Related Topics"

#: templates/privacy.html:64
msgid "法令等に基づく対応"
msgstr "Compliance with Laws and Regulations"

#: templates/privacy.html:73
msgid "第三者提供について"
msgstr "Regarding Third-party Provision"

#: templates/privacy.html:75
msgid "当社は、法令に基づく場合を除き、本人の同意なく第三者へ個人情報を提供いたしません。"
msgstr ""
"Except as required by law, we will not disclose personal information to "
"third parties without the individual’s consent."

#: templates/privacy.html:81
msgid "安全管理"
msgstr "Safety Management"

#: templates/privacy.html:83
msgid "当社は、個人情報への不正アクセス、漏洩、滅失または毀損の防止その他個人情報の安全管理のため、適切な措置を講じます。"
msgstr ""
"We will take appropriate measures to prevent unauthorized access, leakage, "
"loss, or damage to personal information, and to ensure the secure management"
" of such information."

#: templates/privacy.html:89
msgid "委託について"
msgstr "Regarding Consignment"

#: templates/privacy.html:91
msgid "利用目的達成のために必要な範囲で、個人情報の取扱いを外部へ委託する場合があります。この場合、適切な委託管理を行います。"
msgstr ""
"We may outsource the handling of personal information to third parties to "
"the extent necessary to achieve the intended purpose. In such cases, we will"
" ensure appropriate oversight of the outsourcing arrangement."

#: templates/privacy.html:97
msgid "開示・訂正・削除等について"
msgstr "Regarding Disclosure, Correction, Deletion, etc"

#: templates/privacy.html:99
msgid "ご本人から自己の個人情報について、開示、訂正、利用停止、削除等の請求があった場合には、法令に従い適切に対応いたします。"
msgstr ""
"If an individual requests the disclosure, correction, suspension of use, or "
"deletion of their personal information, we will respond appropriately in "
"accordance with applicable laws and regulations."

#: templates/privacy.html:105
msgid "お問い合わせ窓口"
msgstr "Contact Us"

#: templates/privacy.html:108
msgid "個人情報の取扱いに関するお問い合わせは、下記窓口までご連絡ください。"
msgstr ""
"For inquiries regarding the handling of personal information, please contact"
" the office listed below."

#: templates/privacy.html:112
msgid "株式会社e-tac　カスタマーサービス係"
msgstr "e-tac Co., Ltd. Customer Service Department"

#: templates/services.html:21
msgid "製造受託業務"
msgstr "Contract Manufacturing Services"

#: templates/services.html:23
msgid "企業様のリソースをコア業務に集中できる環境づくりを構築するため、様々な受託業務に対応いたします。"
msgstr ""
"We offer a wide range of outsourced services to help companies create an "
"environment where they can focus their resources on their core business "
"operations."

#: templates/services.html:25
msgid ""
"システム開発・運用・管理のIT分野の受託をはじめ、金属加工・プラスチック成型・検査・梱包、食品製造等の製造業分野においては、工数・工程・製造個数等、企業様のニーズに応じた業務の受託が可能です。"
msgstr ""
"In addition to providing contract services in the IT sector—including system"
" development, operation, and management—we also offer contract services "
"tailored to the specific needs of our clients in the manufacturing sector, "
"such as metalworking, plastic molding, inspection, packaging, and food "
"production, covering areas such as man-hours, production processes, and "
"production volumes."

#: templates/services.html:35
msgid "これまで弊社では様々な業種の業務受託を行ってまいりました。"
msgstr ""
"To date, our company has provided contract services across a wide range of "
"industries."

#: templates/services.html:37
msgid ""
"各々の業種業態において企業様とともに、業務を通じて問題点や課題を拾い出し、改善提案を行い生産効率の改善や不良発生頻度の低下等に努めてまいりました。"
msgstr ""
"We have worked closely with companies across various industries and business"
" models to identify issues and challenges through our day-to-day operations,"
" and have made improvement proposals to enhance production efficiency and "
"reduce the frequency of defects."

#: templates/services.html:39
msgid "ただ単に業務処理をするのではなく、生産効率を高め、コスト削減を実現いたします。"
msgstr ""
"We don’t just handle routine tasks; we boost productivity and reduce costs."

#: templates/services.html:41
msgid "現場を熟知した弊社だからできる、現場改善型アウトソーシングを提供します。"
msgstr ""
"With our in-depth knowledge of the on-site, we offer on-site improvement "
"outsourcing services that only we can provide."

#: templates/services.html:49
msgid "製造DX支援型アウトソーシング"
msgstr "Outsourcing Services Supporting Manufacturing Digital Transformation"

#: templates/services.html:51
msgid "様々な業種の業務を受託しており、各々の業務・工程等を熟知しております。"
msgstr ""
"We handle projects across a wide range of industries and have a thorough "
"understanding of the specific tasks and processes involved in each."

#: templates/services.html:53
msgid "机上の空論のDX推進ではなく、現場を理解した上でのDX化の取り組みをサポートいたします。"
msgstr ""
"We support DX initiatives based on a thorough understanding of the actual "
"situation, rather than relying on theoretical, impractical approaches."

#: templates/services.html:55
msgid ""
"ただ単にシステム導入等を推し進めるのではなく、現場・人・状況を業務を通じて十分に理解・把握させていただき、実際に運用できるDX推進を提案します。"
msgstr ""
"Rather than simply pushing for the implementation of new systems, we take "
"the time to fully understand and grasp the on-site environment, the people "
"involved, and the specific circumstances through our work, and we propose "
"digital transformation initiatives that can be effectively implemented in "
"practice."

#: templates/terms_of_use.html:25
msgid ""
